title: Schubert - The String Quartets - Leipziger Qt
description:
Schubert: The String Quartets.

You need look no further than this for the perfect set of the complete Schubert String Quartets. The Leipziger Quartet recorded the composer's complete output for this instrument combination in a 9 disc set in the late 1990s. This upload presents the 15 numbered quartets but omits the rest of the set: the minuets and dances, etc. The set was released by MDG and was given the highest praise in the 2002 edition of the Penguin Guide.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
